---
By: Hans Dench
Locus:
  Page: 410
  Verse: 13
Tags:
  - Search
---
Oh, my God, how does it happen. ...thatThou art so great and yet nobody
findsThee, that thou callest so loudly andnobody hears Thee, that Thou art
sonear and nobody feels Thee, that Thougivest Thyself to everybody and
nobodyknows Thy name.
